-- Canadian Wheat Board Begins Offering Farmer Contracts Today
-- B y   W h i t n e y   M c F e r r o n
-- 2012-03-29T15:07:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-29/canadian-wheat-board-begins-offering-farmer-contracts-today.html
Farmers can begin signing up today
with the Canadian Wheat Board for new pool and cash contracts
for wheat, durum and malting barley, the grain marketer said.  The  contracts  apply to the crop year beginning Aug. 1, the
board said today in a  statement  on its website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Whitney McFerron in Chicago at 
 wmcferron1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
